Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.60,Tsuritama_Main,CUSTOMER A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.06,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.08,Tsuritama_Overlap,CUSTOMER A,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.02,Tsuritama_Main,CUSTOMER A,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.02,Tsuritama_Overlap,CUSTOMER B,0000,0000,0000,,Mahi-mahi, mahi-mahi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:12.89,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three weeks \Nsince I started working.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:18.08,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Work is growing on me, \Nbut even more fun than working,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.07,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,is fishing after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.53,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Enoshima bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.76,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. It's a bait ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.46,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Bait ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.39,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,A school of small fish at the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:38.97,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are bigger fish\Nunderneath trying to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.64,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,What's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.78,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Probably tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.04,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've brought my tuna rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.76,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can fish for tuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:47.69,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.47,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:54.86,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:31.92,Ep_Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(529,477)}Horrified Splash
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.80,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, you're quite tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:34.87,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been running \Naround on a boat all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.35,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.52,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm tan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.20,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're \Nalways skipping work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.45,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, Yuki, \Npretending you're the only good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.44,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What, you got a problem \Nwith that? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.51,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Yuki. \NI have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.77,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to leave the \Nhospital by the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.65,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.13,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.34,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.92,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.81,Tsuritama_Overlap,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.95,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.08,goldcat,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Cat Cup
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.08,tuna,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.08,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.66,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.26,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki and I are going to \Ncelebrate Keito's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.29,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:16.21,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to give her a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:19.11,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was thinking fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.16,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:24.07,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch something \Nmyself for her to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.14,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.06,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want\Nto catch? I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.32,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.14,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.59,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.73,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma loves tuna,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.69,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd like to try catching \None at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.09,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna fishing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.24,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,He's carefree, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:49.49,Enoshima,,0000,0000,0000,,In Enoshima
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:51.54,Copy of Enoshima,,0000,0000,0000,,In Enoshima
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:55.33,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, we read your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.19,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.00,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked the local \Npolice about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.29,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,they said the surfers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.05,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,didn't seem to be lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.77,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,We have already received\Ninformation regarding the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.17,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this incident deals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.30,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,with neither aircraft nor sea vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.09,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,When they came to their\Nsenses, time had passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.51,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,and they had moved to \Na different location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:24.94,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it may have something \Nto do with Bermuda Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:28.47,Tsuritama_Overlap,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yamada, we did not instruct you \Nto investigate this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.53,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:33.38,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Continue your assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.67,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.28,Tsuritama_Main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.01,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Enoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.01,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Kamikakushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.93,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Kamikakushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:52.78,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You might want to ask \NGrandpa about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.17,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.55,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.35,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He's the head priest of this shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.86,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also the town mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.57,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.53,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, you just look quite different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.44,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Do I look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.34,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.43,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.09,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.84,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.76,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.38,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun wants to ask you \Nabout the Kamikakushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.26,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.35,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is not to interrupt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.01,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Tapioca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:46.47,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,There's an old legend of this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.03,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,about a dragon who would spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.53,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,people away, and the \Ngoddess who subdued him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.37,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon and a goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.04,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's a load \Nof bull, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.66,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. But, this dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.13,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What does it represent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.14,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon's a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:11.21,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,But dragons are creatures of fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.72,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.31,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.02,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,He really did spirit people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.10,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,It just happens to be peaceful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:23.23,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, I've been \Ngetting a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.14,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.60,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.41,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.54,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you like fish with whiskers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.01,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Like catfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.46,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.17,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I hate jokes... so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.31,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Catfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.61,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're fishing for tuna today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.58,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:07.69,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fishing belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.32,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It'll support your rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.06,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna are big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.75,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without one of these, \Nthey'll take your rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.58,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.41,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use these lures. Pencil bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.42,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Pencil, pencil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.82,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.10,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Because of its simple, pencil-like shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.20,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,just reeling it won't \Ncreate enough action.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:30.51,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wave your rod down like this to \Nmake it sink into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.90,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Make it seem like bait by \Nletting it swim a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.35,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,before pulling it up to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.93,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call jerking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.39,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do this repeatedly to \Nlure the tuna to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:42.10,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you do it right, \Nthe tuna will go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.87,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you bring it to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.98,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.86,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Enoshima bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:54.70,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,The most important part of tuna \Nfishing is accurate casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.63,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.79,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna are cautious, so you \Ncannot approach them easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:04.06,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,To avoid missing your only chance, \Nyou must cast accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.08,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Indian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:08.55,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only important \Npart of catching big fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:11.06,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You need good teamwork between
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.93,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the guy fishing and the \Nguy steering the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.89,Tsuritama_Overlap,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.73,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you hook one, \Ntuna swim fast and pull hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.81,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,If the guy driving the boat sucks, \Nyou'll lose him in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.83,Tsuritama_Overlap,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Catching tuna seems hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.22,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You'll catch one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.85,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The real problem is location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.90,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Location?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:30.06,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Casting and teamwork are both important,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:34.36,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we have to find where they are first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:44.27,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Wave the rod down and let it sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:47.21,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Make it seem like bait by \Nletting it swim a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.71,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,before pulling it up to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.42,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Do this repeatedly to lure the tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:09.19,Tsuritama_Main,CUSTOMER B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bro. There's a ton \Nof birds over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.65,Tsuritama_Main,CUSTOMER B,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.67,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:13.40,Tsuritama_Main,CUSTOMER B,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.03,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as "bright sea"\Nand pronounced Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.53,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an artificial fish reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.67,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Fish reef?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.91,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,A man-made object placed in the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:24.39,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,ocean to encourage fish to live and mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.67,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.13,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place where lots of fish gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.15,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we can't go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.96,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They don't allow fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.38,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they prohibit fishing \Nin a place with lots of fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.91,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,How suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.99,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a secret \Nfishing spot for locals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:43.31,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't actually a fishing ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.20,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But the locals won't go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.11,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.15,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.87,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand around talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:51.61,Tsuritama_Main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.60,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details, but apparently,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.53,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a fishing boat disappeared \Nover there a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.50,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have been working \Nhard this past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.09,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You've all gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.48,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.14,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.39,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.52,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.35,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, bring it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.81,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,He does this every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.27,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to jump in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.03,Tsuritama_Overlap,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong? Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.03,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,He won't let us go until \Nwe do this. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.53,Tsuritama_Main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.23,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.72,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:49.87,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.80,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Your movements are \Nbecoming more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.48,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.88,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,cool supporting character\Nwho gives the fishermen a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.18,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely to the guys fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.05,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,watch their movements carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.43,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,and move the boat into the\Neasiest position for them to fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.08,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll slowly approach bait balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:11.53,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes move to cut the tuna off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.48,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Once they hook one, you close the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.85,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.40,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I have one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.28,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:23.36,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask me anything about boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.53,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Are there tuna at Akemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:27.76,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:30.93,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's been out there recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.38,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Because a boat disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.04,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.38,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted me to \Nteach you how to drive a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.34,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:42.05,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's time to head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.89,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But the sun won't set for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.22,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.25,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the currents are shifting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.21,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've got something to do after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:56.34,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can have someone \Nelse take you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.57,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't go to Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.94,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Under no circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.66,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:00.40,Tsuritama_Main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.30,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.28,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:09.05,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks. None of the boats are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.25,Tsuritama_Main,NATUSKI,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to catch \Ntuna from the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.58,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take my boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.77,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.72,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Enoshima bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.15,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, let me fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:40.54,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I know. This is an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.95,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,We've cast tons of times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.32,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're not in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:50.68,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard of people \Ncatching tuna around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.02,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Should we check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.54,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But the captain said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.95,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but the tuna \Nare definitely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.92,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.63,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to catch one, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:10.43,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely want to catch one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.10,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.19,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:20.03,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to such a great spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.23,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.20,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.83,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, slowly approach the bait ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.24,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:31.91,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.16,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.49,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:39.25,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the distance. \NAre you sure you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:40.75,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.59,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss. You only have one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.26,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? Aim better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.55,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.76,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of casting into the bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.99,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,It's Enoshima bowl, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.00,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.98,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Enoshima bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.57,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.31,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.91,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, jerking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.57,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.70,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Wave the rod down and let it sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.80,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Make it seem like bait by \Nletting it swim a little
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.04,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,before pulling it up to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:15.79,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.65,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,How far is he going to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.72,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for him to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:20.79,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.00,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Won't I run out of line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:23.80,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.98,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.90,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Reel it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.99,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's so... strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.99,Tsuritama_Overlap,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Close the gap, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.55,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.22,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,So close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.06,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm stopping the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:40.81,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,So, so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.23,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.71,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.53,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.45,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki can't do it. Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.33,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Give him one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.09,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the same, no matter \Nhow many times he does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:54.18,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, have some faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.28,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,If Yuki doesn't catch it, it's pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.82,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, Grandma's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.59,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.12,Tsuritama_Main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.09,Tsuritama_Main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.33,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.22,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, wait here like a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.31,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.56,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Try to keep your cool, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.44,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.51,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.90,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you! {\i1}You{\i0} calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.65,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.95,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The tuna quieted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.03,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.12,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Reel it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.08,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.96,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.96,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:45.51,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.38,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.90,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.73,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.30,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.48,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.90,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.51,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You caused so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.73,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Keito will be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.22,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.34,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.61,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.91,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.23,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.66,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.87,Tsuritama_Overlap,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.88,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.84,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.64,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.63,Tsuritama_Overlap,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,He's not moving anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.44,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.60,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.35,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.94,Tsuritama_Main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.54,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They must have lost track \Nof time while fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.95,Tsuritama_Main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Heihachi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.18,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.12,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,The sea god's in a sour mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:01.83,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of those unscrupulous \Nkids who headed into Akemi to fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.49,Tsuritama_Main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.58,Tsuritama_Main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.29,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I found Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.92,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,How did it get so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.48,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:14.97,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,No. We have less fuel, \Nso it must be memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.63,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps memory manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.79,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Manipulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.31,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bait ball! \NI've never seen one so huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.15,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.28,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:35.24,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we meet \Nafter a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.12,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.62,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.92,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.06,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:18:00.12,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Fish, human, alien. Fish, human, \Nalien. Fish, human, alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.10,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:04.39,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally shown your true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.73,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.94,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.73,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.57,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.78,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they weren't at the Koshigoe Dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.95,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,The guys at the yacht harbor\Nhadn't seen them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.46,Tsuritama_Main,TOMATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please do. Search near Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.50,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.80,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Seishunmaru here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.47,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,What a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.43,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Open your mouth and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.48,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.16,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.88,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Enoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.51,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan, I told you it was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.51,Tsuritama_Main,PEOPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.23,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.23,Tsuritama_Overlap,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.90,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who said we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.15,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I said I wanted to fish for tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:35.91,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:36.86,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.15,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.35,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.80,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.49,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:49.30,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the trouble we went through?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:53.96,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea... \Nhow worried I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.00,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad! I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.84,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, Tamocchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.94,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.02,Tsuritama_Main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.27,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.28,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Keito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.57,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:25.28,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I was sad to see summer end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.58,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time I felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:38.02,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.44,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.05,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.63,Tsuritama_Main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:50.10,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see Haru truly smile \Nfor a while after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:55.80,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't find out why \Nuntil a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.03,Tsuritama_Main,CREW A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.13,Tsuritama_Main,CREW B,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yoshizo-san still fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:05.95,Tsuritama_Main,CREW A,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.74,Tsuritama_Main,CREW B,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:10.62,Tsuritama_Main,CREW A,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Enoshima dance.
